An ListView support "pull down refresh" and "pull up load" feature.

How to use:
    Just replace ListView by me.maxwin.XListView.

**Screenshots**
Pull down to refresh:

![Refresh normal](https://github.com/Maxwin-z/XListView-Android/blob/master/screenshots/refresh_normal.png?raw=true)
![Refresh ready](https://github.com/Maxwin-z/XListView-Android/blob/master/screenshots/refresh_ready.png?raw=true)
![Refresh loading](https://github.com/Maxwin-z/XListView-Android/blob/master/screenshots/refresh_loading.png?raw=true)

Pull up to load more:

![Load normal](https://github.com/Maxwin-z/XListView-Android/blob/master/screenshots/load_more_normal.png?raw=true)
![Load ready](https://github.com/Maxwin-z/XListView-Android/blob/master/screenshots/load_more_ready.png?raw=true)
![Load loading](https://github.com/Maxwin-z/XListView-Android/blob/master/screenshots/load_more_loading.png?raw=true)